
// The code snippet demonstrates how to list all files within a specified folder recursively, including hidden files. The [io.file.list-recursively] slot is used with a reference to a folder argument, and options to display hidden files and system files are set through the [display-hidden] and [display-system] slots respectively.
io.file.list-recursively:x:@.arguments/*/folder
   display-hidden:bool:true
   display-system:x:@.arguments/*/sys
